data.description: This Arkansas property has it ALLLLL!!! This beautiful 3 bedroom/2 bath home offers smart space, comfort, beauty and relaxation. Spacious, formal dining perfect for family gatherings or kiddo sleepover pizza space. The kitchen has all the STUFF....granite, stainless appliances, pantry, disposal, CORNER KITCHEN WINDOW!! Living room has a cozy fireplace, room for the big screen tv and large windows to see outback to the....POOL!!! Off of your gated, covered patio, you'll find a refreshing, salt water pool with slide and lounging space. Backyard is fenced and safe for the kiddos while they play basketball on the concrete pad or splash in the pool while your pets run around and play. Master Bathroom has double vanities AND closets..ladies, you will have your own space and a soaker tub!! Somebody get the wine, because we're relaxing both inside and out!! The following is all new--- Pool has new salt cell and pump sand. The pool vacuum does convey. Paint throughout. Flooring. Roof in 2019. HVAC in 2020. Tankless hot water heater in 2020.  Call me for a showing!!
